pair_coeff 2 2 spooff/thermal
pair_coeff 2 2 spooff/hertz 0.5 0.1 0.5
pair_coeff 1 2 spooff/hertz 1 0.1 0.5
pair_coeff 1 2 spooff/thermal

fix fracstrength cyl spooff/setfailure 1 1 0 0 #this set the fracture strain very high so nothing fractures while the large time steps are taken and the system is brough to its new equilibrium stress
fix fracstrength2 clad spooff/setfailure 1 2 0 0 #this set the fracture strain very high so nothing fractures while the large time steps are taken and the system is brough to its new equilibrium stress
run 200000
